<b>SXDrive 0.4.8</b><br>
<br>
Changes in this release include:<br>
- show ETA and transfer speed for uploads and downloads in the tray menu<br>
- AES256 filter improvements for better compatibility with SX 1.2<br>
- add option to check for beta releases<br>
- show deleted files in sync history<br>
- full Retina support on OS X<br>
- improve volume tab layout<br>
- restart all active profiles after an upgrade<br>
- minor fixes and improvements
